ghost-role-information-ifrit-name = Ifrit, the mystagogue's guardian
ghost-role-information-ifrit-description = Powerful guardian's from the noosphere brought forth by a contract between the ifrit and the mystagogue to defend and protect the mystagogue and their department.
ghost-role-information-ifrit-rules = You are an ifrit, a familiar and guardian. You are contracted with the mystagogue, and must follow their commands. You may act on your own will in lieue of instruction, but you are always on the side of the station.
